OL,3,CNumber of children in temporary
OL,4,Chousing could fill Wembley twice,
OL,5,Cfigures show
OL,7,FNew figures reveal the number of
OL,8,Fchildren living in temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation in England could fill
OL,10,FWembley Stadium twice - the highest
OL,11,Flevel since records began.
OL,13,FHousing campaigners have warned the
OL,14,Fgovernment is failing to grapple with
OL,15,Fa growing crisis after quarterly
OL,16,Fhomelessness statistics, published by
OL,17,Fthe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,18,Fand Local Government, showed 172,420
OL,19,Fchildren are now waiting for a
OL,20,Fpermanent home.
