OL,7,FThe figures also show one in every 30
OL,8,Fchildren in England is growing up
OL,9,Fwithout the stability of a permanent
OL,10,Fhome, the highest number since 2004,
OL,11,Faccording to analysis by human rights
OL,12,Fcharity Just Fair.
OL,14,FOverall, there were 84,240 households
OL,15,Fwith children in temporary
OL,16,Faccommodation at the end of June 2025.
