OL,7,F"This is not inevitable; it's a
OL,8,Fpolitical choice," she said. "Housing
OL,9,Fis a human right ` and when 170,000
OL,10,Fchildren are denied that right, it
OL,11,Fputs their health, education and
OL,12,Ffamily life at risk."
OL,14,FThe rise in figures comes despite a
OL,15,Fdrop in child homelessness in previous
OL,16,Fyears. In 2010, the number fell to
OL,17,Funder 70,000.
