OL,7,FDirector of Campaigns and Policy at
OL,8,FShelter, Mairi MacRae, said:
OL,9,F"Thousands face a long grim winter
OL,10,Fstuck in temporary accommodation,
OL,11,Fincluding freezing bedsits and cramped
OL,12,FB&Bs, because successive governments
OL,13,Fhave passed the buck for a housing
OL,14,Femergency of their making.
OL,16,F"Every day we hear from families who
OL,17,Fare terrified of spending months or
OL,18,Feven years in appalling conditions,
OL,19,Fwatching their breath hang in the air
OL,20,Fas damp and mould climbs the walls.
